From the node you wish to join to this cluster, run the following:
microk8s join 10.171.70.146:25000/9b7385c0d4523e73286252f7453dc5ac/3909a40d1175

Use the '--worker' flag to join a node as a worker not running the control plane, eg:
microk8s join 10.171.70.146:25000/9b7385c0d4523e73286252f7453dc5ac/3909a40d1175 --worker

If the node you are adding is not reachable through the default interface you can use one of the following:
microk8s join 10.171.70.146:25000/9b7385c0d4523e73286252f7453dc5ac/3909a40d1175
microk8s join fd42:94:e41e:89e9:216:3eff:fe50:1114:25000/9b7385c0d4523e73286252f7453dc5ac/3909a40d1175
